data.description: This stunning craftsman home with a front porch is nested in a quiet cul de sac in a very sought after subdivision of Berry Springs Bethlehem. Close to Hwy 316. This home offers a luxurious hardwood floor on the main that leads to the living room and opens to the amazing kitchen with stained cabinets showing a beautiful white backsplash in the background. Large kitchen Island, SS appliances, plus a guest bedroom tucked in the corner with a full bathroom for visitors. In Addition to all that the home comes with a big loft upstairs , an extra bonus room and a game or study room on the main. Plus, the laundry opens upp to another closet that you can use for ur extra clothing. Open floor concept. Come check it out. It will not last.
